en_162661_0	Former Senior DIG Anura Senanayake who was in remand for over a year for allegedly concealing evidence linked to the murder of ruggerite Wasim Thajudeen, has been released on strict bail conditions.
en_162661_1	The suspect was released on one million rupees cash bail and three surety bails of 5 million rupees.
en_162661_2	The Judge ordered that one of such sureties should be a close relative of the suspect.
